{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/EN-\u6b22\u8fce\u6765\u5230\u6c90\u6708\u5c71\u8c37.png?t=1734926190\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Welcome to Moonlit Valley!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your grandmother has left you a delightful surprise\u2014a vacation lodge in the heart of a mysterious valley, Jacaranda Mansion!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Nestled in a secluded southwest valley, home mostly to ladies, it\u2019s a hidden paradise with a rich cultural heritage. But beyond the familiar scents of home, there are secrets here\u2014secrets tied to the lost myths you once heard from your grandmother as a child...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The immediate goal is clear: use the valley\u2019s magical farming techniques and mysterious\u00a0technologies\u00a0to revive Jacaranda Mansion\u2019s former glory! But with so much to explore, you\u2019re free to set your own goals and chart your journey as you and the sisterhood discover the countless wonders of Moonlit Valley together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As for your grandmother\u2019s whereabouts? Don\u2019t worry; she\u2019s simply taken off on an impromptu road trip, riding her motorcycle into the horizon!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/EN-\u91cd\u6574\u5c71\u5e84\u4e4b\u8def.png?t=1734926190\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/1.png?t=1734926190\" />Cultivate southwest specialty crops with creative grafting!\u00a0Enjoy an alchemical experience that\u2019s impossible to put down!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/2_1_.png?t=1734926190\" />Raise adorable animal friends<i>\u2026</i>\u00a0and, of course, don\u2019t miss the fishing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/3.png?t=1734926190\" />\u00a0Cook\u00a0to your heart\u2019s content!\u00a0Choose from a variety\u00a0of ingredients and techniques. Let your culinary mastery\u00a0make the restaurant a local legend\u2026 (But if it fails, well, it\u2019s all part of the fun!)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/\u70f9\u996a.gif?t=1734926190\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/4.png?t=1734926190\" />Furnish Jacaranda Mansion\u00a0with unique pieces\u00a0to attract more guests!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/\u623f\u95f41.jpg?t=1734926190\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/1280X1280.png?t=1734926190\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/5.png?t=1734926190\" /><i>\u00a0</i>Run your own souvenir shop!\u00a0Design one-of-a-kind products inspired by your discoveries in the valley!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/6.png?t=1734926190\" />Overwhelmed?\u00a0As the boss, you can always hire more hands! Recruit staff to help grow the mansion\u2019s success.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/EN-\u5c71\u8c37\u4e2d\u7684\u60a0\u54c9\u65e5\u5e38.png?t=1734926190\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img